## Naming rules

- Top-level directory names use kebab-case
- Never nest projects: no `foo/foo/` patterns
- New services without source go as `<service-name>/` with a `docker-compose.yml`
- New applications go as `<project-name>/` with their own build files
- Dead projects move to `_archive/` with a note in `_archive/README.md`
